          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "<br><p>When used as directed, these ingredients work synergistically and safely at low doses without risk of  dependence or tolerance. Tro Calm also contains <a href=\"https://troscriptions.com/blogs/main/cannabidiol-cbd\" style=\"  text-decoration: underline;\">CBD</a> and <a href=\"https://troscriptions.com/blogs/main/cannabigerol-cbg\" style=\" text-decoration: underline;\">CBG</a>, which modulate the GABergic and  endocannabinoid systems.</p> <p>The result of this novel formula? 1⁄4 troche will take the edge off and you’ll perform better, 1⁄2 troche and  you’ll be more chill (think a glass or two of wine without the downside), 3⁄4 to 1 full troche for full relaxation,  full quieting of the mind, and deeper sleep.</p>"
