    "rich_text_g9rYtt": {
      "type": "rich-text-v2",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_FmeD6i": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "GABA Benefits and Side Effects",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker",
            "horizontal_span": 1
          }
        },
        "text_HCeCNn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>GABA supplements have been explored for their potential to support mental and physical health by promoting relaxation, improving sleep, and reducing anxiety. However, users should be aware of possible side effects, which can range from mild digestive issues to more pronounced drowsiness or muscle weakness. It's crucial to consider these factors when deciding to use GABA supplements as part of a wellness or healing regimen</p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker",
