        },
        "text_FRyKBg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Given the limitations associated with traditional GABA supplements, particularly their difficulty in crossing  the blood-brain barrier effectively, buccal troches emerge as a superior alternative, especially when they contain allosteric and orthosteric compounds that enhance GABA. </p><p>Buccal troches allow direct absorption into the bloodstream, bypassing the digestive system and enhancing bioavailability. This delivery method not only maximizes the potential benefits of GABA without the common side effects associated with oral supplements but also offers a more efficient and user-friendly approach to leveraging the calming effects of GABA. </p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
